original_title: Holy Hell! or: A Profound Tale of Evil and Satanic Wickedness
overview: Cthulhu, better known as his human form Daniel, gathers his local New Jersey Satanic Persuasion chapter for their weekly night of fun and festivity. But tonight's meeting is a special occasion: there's a new member joining the gang. And, tonight, Joel will perform the sacrificial induction ceremony as he sacrifices a willing human to the dark lord himself.
tagline: Glorious Liquids Never Tasted So Good
title: Holy Hell! or: A Profound Tale of Evil and Satanic Wickedness
